          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "As powder targets were made by deposition from an",
                " ethanol suspension.",
                "The thickness (~60 mg/cm2) was calculated from the",
                " known weight of the As powder and the diameter of the",
                " deposit.",
                "An acetone-Zapon solution was used to fix the As",
                " deposit to the filter paper backing.",
                "The filter paper was glued to an Al frame which was as",
                " thick as the deposit and had a centered hole.",
                "The remaining open side was covered with a thin Mylar",
                " foil to prevent any target material from sticking to",
                " the adjacent Al degrader foil."
              ]
            }
          ],
